{"tid":1597243,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"比特幣跌穿8000！有沒有平的交易平台？","createTime":"2019-09-27T01:01:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T16:23:38.000Z","uid":324930,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f0371c0dd629f2b27a46886895a873fe522c099a","tid":1597243,"uid":324930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T01:01:18.000Z","msg":"想投機一下"},{"pid":"52ba5c1bdbc0c2e13ff0afbf7bfae337f13e17ed","tid":1597243,"uid":79793,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T01:03:32.000Z","msg":"星火呢個平台唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb2653db9a00dbb4b6baa13d3592d1c879fbf144","tid":1597243,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T01:26:42.000Z","msg":"plus500"},{"pid":"a58389ce16f544d4bc7eadb905919e9787e43c04","tid":1597243,"uid":94093,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T02:07:35.000Z","msg":"新手入金全攻略<br />\n<br />\n利申: 本人與以下所有公司/平台都沒有任何利益關係，只是綜合自己及朋友的經驗，推薦幾個使用體驗較佳的公司/平台(排名絕對分先後)<br />\n<br />\n小額(幾千至幾萬)<br />\n<br />\n1. 火幣 (國產)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.huobi.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huobi.com%2F&d=6kTjEm0JFzAR16ySTE8tYi1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=e3dac598\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.huobi.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n好處: 支付方法多元化，本地銀行過數/FPS/Wechat Pay/AliPay都得，交易速度快<br />\n<br />\n壞處: 開戶口麻煩要提交好多文件，價格與市價偏差大，有騙徒出現，必須要自行衡量風險，not very user friendly，不適合新手。<br />\n<br />\n建議當市況轉為平靜，有閒錢而見到有價錢平的不妨先買定。<br />\n<br />\n2. HKBX ‪(&lrm;香港區塊鏈交易所‬)<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkbx.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkbx.hk&d=6kTjEm0JFzAR16ySTE8tYi1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=2ba3d159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkbx.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n好處: 屬於香港本土公司，手續費 &amp; 價格貼市合理，本地銀行過數，可以用港幣即時買賣，提供買賣&amp;托管服務，公司經營多年信譽良好，不用擔心遇上騙徒。<br />\n<br />\n壞處: 需要身份驗證，介面設計不太吸引，暫時只提供買賣BTC and LTC。<br />\n<br />\n3. Myethshop<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.myethshop.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.myethshop.com&d=6kTjEm0JFzAR16ySTE8tYi1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=ab9d5dfd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.myethshop.com</a><br />\n<br />\n好處: 屬於香港本土公司，本地銀行過數，可以用港幣即時買賣，公司經營多年信譽良好, 不用擔心遇上騙徒<br />\n<br />\n壞處: 需要身份驗證，買賣價格稍貴<br />\n<br />\n4. Tidebit <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.tidebit.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tidebit.com&d=6kTjEm0JFzAR16ySTE8tYi1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=b90cfe4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.tidebit.com</a><br />\n<br />\n好處: 可以親自上公司直接入港幣現金， 亦可以提出港幣(親身入港幣不用手續費，提取港幣則要0.1%+50港幣的手續費)<br />\n<br />\n壞處: 需要身份驗證，交易所少人用，交易差價大，交易系統時常有問題， 宣傳手法有很多問題，旗下公司TiDeal出現很多問題及負評<br />\n<br />\n6. Bitcoin ATM<br />\n<br />\n好處: 不用身份驗證，港幣現金交易<br />\n<br />\n壞處: 超級貴，超級貴， 級貴！<br />\n<br />\n7. 與網友p2p交易<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/Fh5gYRbY-Yn3JwZ4UZJYsA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FFh5gYRbY-Yn3JwZ4UZJYsA&d=6kTjEm0JFzAR16ySTE8tYi1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=6c6d0bea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/Fh5gYRbY-Yn3JwZ4UZJYsA</a><br />\n<br />\n好處: 價格雙方協定，一般會比經平台/公司好<br />\n<br />\n壞處: 時常有騙徒出現，必須要自行衡量風險。如果是大額現金面交更要小心被打劫風險(香港外國都時有發生)。<br />\n<br />\n8. Coinbase (美國)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.coinbase.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.coinbase.com%2F&d=6kTjEm0JFzAR16ySTE8tYi1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=c1ed1aaf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.coinbase.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n好處:公司經營多年信譽良好，不用擔心遇上騙徒，可以直接買好多唔同幣種BTC，ETH，BNB，XRP，LTC，BCH &amp; ABC etc.<br />\n<br />\n壞處: 除咗用信用卡俾錢之外佢哋係唔會支持用港幣直接買的。<br />\n價格 &amp; 手續費貴，開戶口麻煩要提交好多文件，要有美金同美國戶口先買到手續費貴再加上兌換美金 and 電匯又要再收多一叢手續費，最重要通常要等兩至三日啲錢先會到交易戶口不能即時。<br />\n<br />\n9. Binance<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.binance.com/en/creditcard\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.binance.com%2Fen%2Fcreditcard&d=6kTjEm0JFzAR16ySTE8tYi1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=94b2a28d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.binance.com/en/creditcard</a><br />\n<br />\n好處: 信用卡過數，一個字: 快。可以直接買BTC，ETH，BNB，XRP，LTC，BCH，ABC <br />\n<br />\n壞處: 價格 &amp; 手續費貴，開戶口麻煩要提交好多文件，唔會支持用港幣直接買的。<br />\n<br />\n*****電匯到外國交易所******<br />\n<br />\n太大額，太頻繁的電匯會引起銀行懷疑你洗黑錢而中止戶口，如果你有按揭戶口在該銀行，絕對要小心，因為中止戶口會要求你立即清還所有貸款。電匯有時會出問題，會好慢(有人試過d錢卡左幾個月)。需要身份驗證，有些交易所身份驗證需時很久。<br />\n<br />\n都係建議用返本地嘅交易所比較穩陣"},{"pid":"50e1e6646080e35a076a9b047855ae6c1a524b82","tid":1597243,"uid":28068,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:09:19.000Z","msg":"又做媒呃人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f3c1fc80abf82c0651022e26335be1a5cbae650","tid":1597243,"uid":300915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:34:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c878164c66f66cf7c3802e0fc7f6a3d643b186a","tid":1597243,"uid":78304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:42:35.000Z","msg":"量子電腦都出，仲比特幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54558cac3b10014e6e43c45a5a55982cf7d4a9cc","tid":1597243,"uid":90497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T16:18:03.000Z","msg":"妹下妹下感 妹左成日都未穿"},{"pid":"5c75668f771fec6bb2b7a41ba0ad9cf7e6e51167","tid":1597243,"uid":45350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T16:23:38.000Z","msg":"星火收唔收bitcoin?"}]}